- Chu Yu!

00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:16.240
Chu Yu!

00:29:17.110 --> 00:29:17.960
Ayo. Aku di sini.

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:19.440
- Jika aku menangkapmu,
- Kau pikir kau bisa?

00:29:19.440 --> 00:29:20.340
Anda akan menyesalinya!

00:29:20.340 --> 00:29:22.080
